# Git Commits

- **Never** add `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>` to commit messages.
- When committing: use `GIT_EDITOR` to avoid editor injection, e.g.:
  `echo "message" > /tmp/msg.txt && GIT_EDITOR="cp /tmp/msg.txt" git commit -F /tmp/msg.txt`
  or for amend: `GIT_EDITOR="cp /tmp/msg.txt" git commit --amend`
- Push after each global change.
